MISCELLANEOUS DISMISSALS

2007-1827. State v. Lothes.

Portage App. No. 2006-P-0086, 2007-Ohio-4266. This cause is pending before the court as an appeal from the Court of Appeals for Portage County. Upon consideration of appellant’s application for dismissal,

*1419It is ordered by the court that the application for dismissal is granted. Accordingly, this cause is dismissed.
